            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Simple way: access `current_app` proxy only when application context is available (during request, in view functions or in functions called by views).\n\nComplex way: put app definition in another module and import app from another module. Drawbacks: you'll have to create a new module to _join_ modules (otherwise you'll create circular imports) and this doesn't work with app factories.\n"
        },
