            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "No, you can't. Doing so will break things. Use an app factory, and do not to stuff globally that needs an app context - whenever you need to access the app somewhere else you can get it via `current_app`.\r\n\r\nAlso, please use IRC or Stack Overflow for questions - this is not the right place."
